metadata.name: FUUJIN RAIJIN
metadata.description:
Wind god and Thunder god in sneakers :)

Drawn with bruch and ink, coloured by digital tool.
WIND and THUNDER in Japanese on their background.

Ukiyoe style with a bit of modern taste.

*Ukiyoe is a genre of Japanese art which flourished from the 17th through 19th centuries. They produced woodblock prints and paintings.

Thank you!

Mia  ( miacomart )
